			<div class="commentcount">93</div>

				<p>Just made these, and they are scrumptious!!  </p>
<p>Note to other readers: I like my cookies crispy, so I let them cook until they were JUST starting to brown on the edges.  They were crispy all the way through, even in the middle.  Perfect for me!  If you want a softer cookie, take them out as directed.  They wont seem done (may even jiggle a little), but once out of the oven, they harden up.    </p>
<p>Thanks for the wonderful recipe.  Definitely a keeper.</p>
