				<p>This is the BEST peanutbutter cookie recipe that I have ever used.  I like most people have modified this recipe to my personal liking.  I omitt the rolling in the sugar and peanutbutter chips and have found using Kirkland brand organic peanutbutter (Costco brand) to make the best tasting cookie.  I also use Ghirardelli Milk Chocolate chips to add even more taste.  What ever modifcations you make to this recipe it will always taste great with the 1 cup of peanutbutter and real vanilla extract.</p>
